Requisição HTTP

url: https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon
    {ip} {path = caminho de indentificação de recurso}

ip: https://pokeapi.co
    http://127.0.0.1:3000    

Request: Method: GET | POST | PUT | DELETE 

Get --> Buscar pokemon
Post -- > Inserir pokemon
Put --> Atualiza Pokemon
Delete --> Deletar pokemon 


string de busca -->  url: https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?type=grass exemplo( pega todos polemons de tipo grama)
string de busca -->  url: https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?type=grass&name=i exemplo( pega todos polemons de tipo grama com a inicial do nome i)

Request Headers --> Configurações
    accept-language: pt-br, pt;q=0,9, en-us; q=0.8, en;q=0.7, gj;q=0.6

Response Headers -->
    content-type: application/json

Body {
    "name": "Test
}

Status cody: 201

